briefdescription.para: Class that determines an ephemeris from tabulated data.

detaileddescription.para: Class that determines an ephemeris from tabulated data, by using numerical interpolation of this data. Required input to this class is a OneDimensionalInterpolator, which may be reset. This class may for instance be used for setting the numerically integrated state of a body as its 'new' ephemeris
